## STEP 3 — Update `src/App.jsx`

Click the `src` folder → click `App.jsx` → ✏️ edit → **select all, delete** → paste the **entire contents** of the `one-on-one-feedback-system.jsx` file I gave you (the updated one with the Google URL already inside it).

Click **Commit changes** ✅

---

## STEP 4 — Create `src/main.jsx` (NEW FILE)

Click **Add file → Create new file** → in the name box type exactly:
```
import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client'
import App from './App.jsx'

ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root')).render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <App />
  </React.StrictMode>
)
```

Click **Commit new file** ✅

---

## STEP 5 — Create `vite.config.js` (NEW FILE)

Click **Add file → Create new file** → name it:
```
vite.config.js
import { defineConfig } from 'vite'
import react from '@vitejs/plugin-react'

export default defineConfig({
  plugins: [react()]
})
```

Click **Commit new file** ✅

